---
title: FinalShell 技术支持与教程
layout: layout.njk
description: "FinalShell 中文下载站教程索引：核心 pillar 教程与参考文章分区，涵盖安装、连接、SFTP、隧道与故障排查。"
pagination:
  data: collections.blog
  size: 10
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
permalink: "blog/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page-{{ pagination.pageNumber }}/{% endif %}index.html"
---

<main class="list-container" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 10px 0;">
    <h1 style="font-size:1.6rem;color:#075E54;border-bottom:2px solid #eee;padding-bottom:12px;">FinalShell 教程知识库</h1>
    <p style="color:#666;margin-bottom:24px;">核心教程优先收录；自动化参考文默认 noindex，仅供站内阅读。</p>

    {% if pagination.pageNumber == 0 %}
    <section style="margin-bottom:32px;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#128C7E;">核心教程</h2>
        <ul style="line-height:2;padding-left:20px;">
        {% for post in collections.indexablePosts %}
            {% if 'cn-finalshell-' in post.fileSlug %}
            <li><a href="{{ post.url }}" style="color:#222;text-decoration:none;">{{ post.data.title }}</a></li>
            {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </section>
    {% endif %}

    <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#128C7E;">{% if pagination.pageNumber == 0 %}最新文章{% else %}文章列表{% endif %}</h2>

    <style>
        .article-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 25px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .article-item { 
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px; 
            background: #f8f9fa; 
            border-left: 4px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .article-item:hover { 
            background: #fff;
            border-left-color: var(--accent-green, #128C7E); 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }
        .item-title { margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 1.3rem; }
        .item-title a { color: #222; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
        .item-title a:hover { color: var(--accent-green, #128C7E); }
        
        .item-meta { color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; display: flex; gap: 15px; }
        .item-excerpt { color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6; }

        .pagination-nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-top: 50px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 2px solid #f4f4f4; }
        .page-link { padding: 8px 16px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .page-link:hover { border-color: var(--accent-green, #128C7E); color: var(--accent-green, #128C7E); background: #fff; }
        .page-active { padding: 8px 16px; background: var(--main-green, #075E54); color: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--main-green, #075E54); border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .page-disabled { padding: 8px 16px; color: #ccc; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 6px; cursor: not-allowed; }
    </style>

    <div class="article-list">
        {% for post in posts %}
        <article class="article-item">
            <h2 class="item-title">
                <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="item-meta">
                {% if post.date %}
                <span>发布时间：{{ post.date.getFullYear() }}-{{ (post.date.getMonth()+1).toString().padStart(2, '0') }}-{{ post.date.getDate().toString().padStart(2, '0') }}</span>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="item-excerpt">
                {{ post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(120) }}
            </div>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <nav class="pagination-nav">
        {% if pagination.href.previous %}
            <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}" class="page-link">« 上一页</a>
        {% else %}
            <span class="page-disabled">« 上一页</span>
        {% endif %}

        {% for pageEntry in pagination.pages %}
            {% if pagination.pageNumber == loop.index0 %}
                <span class="page-active">{{ loop.index }}</span>
            {% else %}
                <a href="{{ pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] }}" class="page-link">{{ loop.index }}</a>
            {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}

        {% if pagination.href.next %}
            <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}" class="page-link">下一页 »</a>
        {% else %}
            <span class="page-disabled">下一页 »</span>
        {% endif %}
    </nav>
</main>
